data.description: Come on in to 341 Cockspur Road in New Friarsgate! A charming 4 bedroom, 3 bath traditional style home ready for your personal touch! This cutie maximizes space with an efficient floorplan and large partially fenced in back yard. The owner’s suite, a second bedroom and 2 full bathrooms are on the main level while 2 more bedrooms and a full bathroom are upstairs. New flooring can be found throughout the home and both the eat-in kitchen and bathrooms have been updated! Large attic space and building in back yard provide for all of your storage needs. Conveniently located to schools, shopping, Saluda Shoals Park and restaurants!   ??Please join me for an Open House Sunday, November 19 from 12-2!
